'''麻薩諸塞-{}-州'''（{{lang-en|Massachusetts}}，{{IPAc-en|audio=en-us-Massachusetts.ogg|ˌ|m|æ|s|ə|ˈ|tʃ|uː|s|ᵻ|t|s}}，{{IPAc-en|-|z|ᵻ|t|s}}），正式名稱為'''麻薩諸塞邦'''（{{lang|en|Commonwealth of Massachusetts}}）{{efn|除马萨诸塞州外，[[肯塔基州|肯塔基州]]、[[维吉尼亚州|维吉尼亚州]]以及[[宾夕法尼亚州|宾夕法尼亚州]]也可以称为「邦」。}}，-{zh-cn:简称; zh-tw:簡稱; zh-hk:又稱;}-'''麻-{}-州'''、'''麻-{}-省'''，是位於[[美国|美國]][[美國東北部|東北部]]的[[美国州份|州]]，為[[美國革命|美國獨立]]時最初的[[十三殖民地|十三州]]之一，也是[[新英格蘭|新英格蘭]]六州裡人口最密集的一州。东临[[大西洋|大西洋]]及[[缅因湾|缅因湾]]，西南方与[[康乃狄克州|康乃狄克州]]相邻，东南方与[[罗德岛州|罗德岛州]]接壤，东北方则有[[佛蒙特州|佛蒙特州]]，西北方为[[新罕布什尔州|新罕布什尔州]]，西边则是[[纽约州|纽约州]]。[[首府|首府]]及最大城市為[[波士顿|波士頓]]，其亦是整个新英格兰地区的最大城市。该州为[[大波士顿|大波士顿都会区]]的所在地，对全美的历史、学术以及工业发展有着极为深远和巨大的影响<ref name="GreaterBoston">{{cite web |last1=Douglas |first1=Craig |title=Greater Boston gains population, remains 10th-largest region in U.S |url=http://www.bizjournals.com/boston/stories/2010/03/22/daily22.html?page=all |publisher=bizjournals.com |access-date=2015-04-21}}</ref>。其最初以[[农业|农业]]、[[渔业|渔业]]以及[[贸易|贸易]]为经济支柱，<ref>{{cite web |title=Maritime Commerce |url=http://www.nps.gov/nr/travel/maritime/commerce.htm |publisher=National Park Service |access-date=2015-04-21}}</ref>而随着[[工业革命|工业革命]]，该州经济开始向[[制造业|制造业]]转型<ref>{{cite web |title=History of Lowell, Massachusetts |url=http://www.lowell.com/city-of-lowell/lowell-history/ |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100405013026/http://lowell.com/city-of-lowell/lowell-history/ |url-status=dead |archive-date=2010-04-05 |publisher=City of Lowell |access-date=2015-04-21 }}</ref>。到了20世纪，马萨诸塞州[[马萨诸塞奇迹|又开始向服务业转型]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Staying Power: The Future of Manufacturing in Massachusetts |url=http://masstech.org/sites/mtc/files/documents/Staying_Power.pdf |publisher=The Center for Urban and Regional Policy School of Social Science, Urban Affairs, and Public Policy Northeastern University |access-date=2015-04-21 }}</ref>。今天的马萨诸塞州，是全球[[生物技术|生物技术]]、[[工程学|工程]]、[[高等教育|高教]]、[[金融|金融]]以及[[航运|航运]]领域的领导者<ref>{{cite web |title=Housing and Economic Development:Key Industries |url=http://www.mass.gov/hed/economic/industries/ |website=mass.gov |access-date=2015-04-21}}</ref>。

马萨诸塞州最早是英国的殖民地。1620年，[[五月花号|五月花号]]的清教徒建立了[[普利茅斯殖民地|普利茅斯殖民地]]。1630年，以该地原住民[[马萨诸塞人|马萨诸塞人]]而得名的[[馬薩諸塞灣殖民地|馬薩諸塞灣殖民地]]又在波士顿和塞勒姆建立了定居点。1692年，[[塞勒姆_(马萨诸塞州)|塞勒姆]]及其周边地区发生了[[集體歇斯底里|集體歇斯底里]]事件，即[[塞勒姆审巫案|塞勒姆审巫案]]。<ref>{{cite web |title=The 1692 Salem Witch Trials |url=http://www.salemwitchmuseum.com/education |publisher=Salem Witch Trials Museum |access-date=2015-04-21}}</ref>1777年，[[亨利·诺克斯|亨利·诺克斯]]将军在[[斯普林菲尔德_(马萨诸塞州)|春田市]]成立了[[春田兵工厂|春田兵工厂]]，在工业革命期间促进了很多技术的进步，其中包括[[可互换零件|可互换零件]]技术的推广。<ref>{{cite web |title=Springfield Armory: Technology in Transition |url=http://www.nps.gov/spar/learn/education/upload/Springfield%20Technology%20Lesson.pdf |publisher=[[National_Park_Service|National Park Service]] [[United_States_Department_of_the_Interior|United States Department of the Interior]] |access-date=April 21, 2015}}</ref>1786年，谢斯起义爆发，对[[美利坚合众国制宪会议|美利坚合众国制宪会议]]造成了一定的影响。<ref name=shay>{{cite web |title=Shays' Rebellion |url=http://www.ushistory.org/us/15a.asp |publisher=ushistory.org |access-date=April 21, 2015}}</ref>18世纪，由于[[北安普敦_(马萨诸塞州)|北安普敦]]传教士[[喬納森·愛德華茲|喬納森·愛德華茲]]的传教活动，新教会的[[第一次大觉醒|第一次大觉醒]]运动迅速席卷了英国本土及[[十三殖民地|十三殖民地]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=The First Great Awakening—Jonathan Edwards |url=http://www.revival-library.org/pensketches/revivals/1st_edwards.html |archive-url=https://archive.today/20150422014428/http://www.revival-library.org/pensketches/revivals/1st_edwards.html |url-status=dead |archive-date=April 22, 2015 |publisher=revival-library.org |access-date=April 21, 2015 }}</ref>到了18世纪末期，发生在波士顿的[[波士顿倾茶事件|倾茶事件]]成为了美国独立战争的导火索，使得波士顿成为了美国“自由的摇篮”。<ref>{{cite web |title=Faneuil Hall |url=http://www.celebrateboston.com/sites/faneuil-hall.htm |publisher=Celebrateboston.com |access-date=April 21, 2015}}</ref>

马萨诸塞州在整个美国科学、商业和文化中，都扮演了不可或缺的角色。在[[美国内战|美国内战]]之前，马萨诸塞州是[[废奴运动|废奴运动]]、[[禁酒运动|禁酒运动]]<ref>{{cite web |title=The Temperance Issue in the Election of 1840: Massachusetts |url=http://www.teachushistory.org/second-great-awakening-age-reform/articles/temperance-issue-election-1840-massachusetts |publisher=Teachushistory.org |access-date=April 21, 2015}}</ref>和[[超验主义|超验主义]]<ref>{{cite book |last1=Packer |first1=Barbara |title=The Transcendentalists |publisher=University of Georgia Press; First edition (April 25, 2007) |isbn=978-0820329581|year=2007 }}</ref>运动的中心。<ref>{{cite web |title=Images of the Antislavery Movement in Massachusetts |url=http://www.masshist.org/online/abolition/index.php |publisher=Masshist.org |access-date=April 21, 2015}}</ref>而[[篮球|篮球]]和[[排球|排球]]这两项运动皆于19世纪末期诞生于马萨诸塞州，篮球诞生于[[斯普林菲尔德_(马萨诸塞州)|春田]]，排球诞生于[[霍利奥克_(马萨诸塞州)|霍利奥克]]。<ref name=basketball>{{cite web |title=Springfield College: The Birthplace of Basketball |url=http://www.springfieldcollege.edu/welcome/birthplace-of-basketball/#.VTa-7CFVhBc |publisher=Springfieldcollege.edu |access-date=April 21, 2015 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150504211534/http://www.springfieldcollege.edu/welcome/birthplace-of-basketball/#.VTa-7CFVhBc |archive-date=May 4, 2015 }}</ref><ref name=volleyball>{{cite web |title=The International Volleyball Hall of Fame |url=http://www.volleyhall.org/about-us.html |publisher=Volleyball.org |access-date=April 21, 2015}}</ref>2004年，马萨诸塞州成为了全美第一个承认[[同性婚姻|同性婚姻]]的州。<ref name=CNNmarriage>{{cite news |title=Massachusetts court strikes down ban on same-sex marriage |url=http://www.cnn.com/2003/LAW/11/18/gay.marriage.reut/ |access-date=April 21, 2015 |agency=Reuters |date=November 18, 2003}}</ref>美国很多政治家族都来自马萨诸塞州，其中包括[[亚当斯家族|亚当斯家族]]和[[肯尼迪家族|肯尼迪家族]]。位于该州的[[哈佛大学|哈佛大学]]为美国历史最悠久的大学，<ref>{{cite web |title=History of Harvard University |url=http://www.harvard.edu/history |publisher=[[Harvard_University|Harvard University]] |access-date=April 21, 2015}}</ref>同时也是捐赠基金最多的大学，<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2015/01/29/us/harvards-endowment-remains-biggest-of-all.html?_r=0 |title=Harvard's Endowment Remains Biggest of All |author=Tamar Lewin |newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |date=January 28, 2015 |access-date=March 6, 2015}}</ref>目前[[美国最高法院|美国最高法院]]很多法官都毕业于[[哈佛法学院|哈佛法学院]]。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/2016/03/16/merrick-garland-supreme-court-obama-nominee/81529760/ |title=Meet Merrick Garland, Obama's Supreme Court nominee |author=Richard Wolf |newspaper=[[USA_Today|USA Today]] |date=March 16, 2016 |access-date=March 16, 2016}}</ref>剑桥的肯德尔广场被称为“地球上最具创新精神的一平方英里”，因为自2010年以来，该广场附近出现了大量创业型初创企业。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://kendallsquare.mit.edu/|title=Kendall Square Initiative|publisher=MIT|access-date=December 1, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://archive.boston.com/business/innovation/blogs/inside-the-hive/2013/05/02/when-neighborhood-crowned-the-most-innovative-square-mile-the-world-how-you-keep-that-way/B1QxCjswQZZuG21WBdyBWK/blog.html|title=When a neighborhood is crowned the most innovative square mile in the world, how do you keep it that way?|author=Lelund Cheung|website=The Boston Globe|access-date=December 3, 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161202165650/http://archive.boston.com/business/innovation/blogs/inside-the-hive/2013/05/02/when-neighborhood-crowned-the-most-innovative-square-mile-the-world-how-you-keep-that-way/B1QxCjswQZZuG21WBdyBWK/blog.html|archive-date=December 2, 2016|url-status=dead}}</ref>哈佛大学和[[麻省理工学院|麻省理工学院]]均位于马萨诸塞州[[剑桥_(马萨诸塞州)|剑桥]]，二者均为世界上最受尊敬的学术机构之一。<ref name="AcademicRanking2">[https://www.timeshighereducation.com/world-university-rankings/2016/reputation-ranking#!/page/0/length/25/sort_by/rank_label/sort_order/asc/cols/rank_only] ''Times Higher Education''. Accessed December 3, 2016.</ref>《世界人口评论》称，马萨诸塞州居民的平均智商超过104，<ref name=MassachusettsHighestIQ>{{cite web|url=https://worldpopulationreview.com/state-rankings/average-iq-by-state|publisher=World Population Review|quote=The highest-ranking state in terms of average IQ is Massachusetts, with an average IQ score of 104.3|access-date=October 1, 2021|title=Average IQ by State}}</ref>是美国所有州中最高的，该州公立学校学生的学习成绩在世界上名列前茅。<ref name="AcademicRanking3" />该州一直被列为美国最宜居的州之一，也是生活成本最高的州之一。<ref name="best states">
